"Peter Graves 8th Baron Graves" 0 Peter George Wellesley Graves, 8th Baron Graves (21 October 1911 – 6 June 1994), was an English actor. Born in London, Graves was the son of Henry Algernon Claude Graves, 7th Baron Graves. Admiral Thomas Graves, 1st Baron Graves, was his great-great-great-grandfather. He was educated at Harrow.
